reviewText: After watching this movie for 30 minutes I turned it off.There was not enough action and it was very slow and boring.Not worth watching,the characters were not introduced properly didn't know who who was who or their purpose my time can be spent elsewhere doing something worthwhile rather than watching a slow boring movie as this.Too many other movie that are much better.
